{"id": 1164, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都做过哪些“收不抵支”的事情？", "description": "吃饭只要五分钟，但做饭洗碗却要俩小时，想来有点不划算。（题图来自：Chris Sasaki）", "record_count": 4675, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160810203333n2YkDV4H7lQRpruF.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-22T02:56:47Z", "options": [{"id": 109824, "content": "著名景点", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270234}, {"id": 109825, "content": "吃胖只用了两天，减肥却用了半个月。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217123}, {"id": 110593, "content": "努力减肥成功一个礼拜不节制饮食就反弹～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679121}, {"id": 109826, "content": "追了半年的对象，处两天就分手了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548295}, {"id": 109827, "content": "暑假作业写了两个月，老师一节课改完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714133}, {"id": 109828, "content": "精心筹备大半年的婚礼，一天就完事儿了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 727133}, {"id": 109829, "content": "花了两小时的妆见网友，见面招呼都不想打直接转身走了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548295}, {"id": 109831, "content": "为了谈恋爱，从北京搬到上海，搬过来三个月就分手了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162244}, {"id": 109832, "content": "练了一暑假的路考，一分钟就被考官撵下车了，不及格！", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666658}, {"id": 109833, "content": "洗澡半小时 出汗秒秒钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223477}, {"id": 109834, "content": "五一放假三天去旅游，路程两天，玩了一天！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726466}, {"id": 109835, "content": "谈了很久的恋爱，都要考虑结婚了，说分手就分手了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723108}, {"id": 109836, "content": "花了好多钱买的衣服没穿两天过季了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684884}, {"id": 118540, "content": "刷鞋两小时，可以下雨，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769047}, {"id": 109837, "content": "花好多钱买的衣服没穿两天就过季了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684884}, {"id": 109838, "content": "追了一年終於追到的男生 三個月厭倦提出分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723392}, {"id": 109839, "content": "吃了一天的饭，五分钟就拉完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 727250}, {"id": 109840, "content": "心动只是一瞬间，爱却要用很多时间来付出", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91118}, {"id": 109842, "content": "  等了120s广告 发现这集看过了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193350}, {"id": 122898, "content": "天门山缆车排队四个半小时 上山半小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790501}, {"id": 109843, "content": "美白大半年，一天就晒黑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686157}, {"id": 109845, "content": "洗澡化妆吹头发换衣服打车花费时间三小时，拍一张一寸照片一分钟就搞定了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680828}, {"id": 109846, "content": "小会计三千五一个月，学费要两万，四年制?", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724682}, {"id": 110621, "content": "用一天的时间来荒废", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732127}, {"id": 109855, "content": "读书一个月，一秒全忘光。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 727321}, {"id": 109856, "content": "零食一包，减肥一天。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709982}, {"id": 109857, "content": "读书十余载，一秒全忘光。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 727321}, {"id": 109858, "content": "花好几万读的大学，学的专业，毕业后一秒钟都没用过！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372166}, {"id": 109859, "content": "存了几t资源，撸完只用三分钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620977}, {"id": 109860, "content": "为了抄近路开一条不熟悉的小道，结果走错路多绕了几公里", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68429}, {"id": 109862, "content": "三天打鱼 两天晒网", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250525}, {"id": 109866, "content": "闲了两分钟所以打开好奇心然后花了半个小时刷了一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 79433}, {"id": 109868, "content": "永远清空不了购物车", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584191}, {"id": 111661, "content": "逛街几个小时买的衣服，回家一看，靠，丑爆了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738397}, {"id": 109875, "content": "上课认真上，暑假认真忘", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700119}, {"id": 109876, "content": "上课认真上，暑假认真忘", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700119}, {"id": 109877, "content": "用了半天拣和洗干巴菌，吃完只需半小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709159}, {"id": 109878, "content": "運動後吃飽飽", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688259}, {"id": 109880, "content": "上亿的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 727416}, {"id": 109881, "content": "花太多时间关注想买的东西，结果想想自己没钱，最后没买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713672}, {"id": 109882, "content": "上亿的种子种错了地方没收获。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 727416}, {"id": 109883, "content": "认认真真复习了一天，2个小时的考试就考砸了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714890}, {"id": 110395, "content": "花了很多机票车票钱去外地找工作却没找到工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672314}, {"id": 109884, "content": "维度不同而予！做饭这件事本身的意义，比所谓的时间成本，也许重要的多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675271}, {"id": 109887, "content": "制作定格动画", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225788}, {"id": 109888, "content": "厕所两分钟，排队半小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222204}, {"id": 109889, "content": "刷信用卡买了一台Mac pro，工资只有5K", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 388577}, {"id": 109890, "content": "做好人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671300}, {"id": 110146, "content": "挣的工资不抵精神损失费。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729051}, {"id": 109891, "content": "上班两个月买不起一张头等舱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725098}]}